    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Weapon Type: Katana </p><p>Weapon (Katana), Legendary Requires attunement You gain a +3 bonus to attack and damage rolls made with this chakra-infused weapon.</p><p>It also gains the Reach 3 property.</p><p>The Sword of Kusanagi is a powerful weapon that cut through almost anything, its blade can extend to reach targets impossible for other melee weapons.</p><p>The Katana has 4 charges, you can spend these charges as a bonus action to cast living weapon on the sword upcasted at S-rank, at no cost.</p><p>The sword recovers 1d4+1 charges at dawn.</p><p></p>",
